name: EnergizeMe
0:
”Alexa open Energize Me”

”Alexa tell Energize Me to give me a tip”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: energize me
des:
Feeling drowsy or sleepy throughout the day? If coffee and energy drinks aren't your thing or just aren't working, the app 'Energize Me' can help. Open the app and Alexa will give you tricks and tips on how to regain energy during the day.

Disclaimer: The information in this skill is for educational and informational purposes only. 

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Energize Me" or "Alexa, open Energize Me" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
